axis0.name: #{Classification}
axis0.text:
CASE
-- No quantity match if order quantity is 0
WHEN "EKPO"."MENGE" = 0.0 THEN 'No order quantity'
WHEN-- Quantity match

    --Order Quantity = GR Quantity
    (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))
    -- Order Quantity = IR Quantity
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))
    -- IR Quantity = GR Quantity (with tolerance of Order Quanitty)
  AND (((1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE")) - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE")) - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))

-- Value match 
--(Price per Unit (PO) - Price per Unit (Invoice) >= -price increase tolerance (diff is negative when price increases) 
--and Price per Unit (PO) - Price per Unit (Invoice) <= price decrease tolerance (diff is positive when price decreases))
    AND(((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE) - (PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."WRBTR")/PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) >= (-1*((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE)*(<%=tolerance_high_price%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE) - (PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."WRBTR")/PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) <= (((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE)*(<%=tolerance_low_price%>/100.00))))
THEN 'Full Match'
    WHEN(    --Order Quantity = GR Quantity
    (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S'))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))
    -- Order Quantity = IR Quantity
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))
    -- GR Quantity = IR Quantity (with tolerance of Order Quanitty)
    AND (((1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S')) - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) >= (-1*((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE") *(<%=tolerance_high_quantity%>/100.00)))) 
    AND (((1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","EKBE"."MENGE","EKBE"."VGABE"='1' AND "EKBE"."SHKZG" = 'S')) - (1.0*PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) <= (((1.0*"EKPO"."MENGE")*(<%=tolerance_low_quantity%>/100.00))))
)
    THEN 'Only Quantity Match'
    WHEN
        ((((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE) - (PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."WRBTR")/PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) >= (-1*((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE)*(<%=tolerance_high_price%>/100.00)))) AND
        (((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE) - (PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."WRBTR")/PU_SUM("EKPO","RSEG"."MENGE"))) <= (((<%=netwr%>/EKPO.MENGE)*(<%=tolerance_low_price%>/100.00)))))
    THEN 'Only Price Match'
    ELSE 'No Match'
END

buttons.variableValue: CASE WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") >= 0 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 THEN 'a) 0 - 100 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 100 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500 THEN 'b) 100 - 500 <%=currency_symbol%>' WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 1500 THEN 'c) 500 - 1.500 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 1500 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 5000 THEN 'd) 1.500 - 5.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  WHEN PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") > 5000 AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 10000 THEN 'd) 5.000 - 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>'  ELSE 'e) > 10.000 <%=currency_symbol%>' END

variables.title: Dimensionbutton_Overview

AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 100 
THEN 'a) 0 - 100 <%=currency_symbol%>'

AND PU_SUM("EKKO","EKPO"."NETWR_CONVERTED") <= 500

variables.name: Three_way_match_filter
variables.value:
Filter PROCESS EQUALS 'Record Goods Receipt';
Filter PROCESS EQUALS 'Record Invoice Receipt';

variables.name: filter7
variables.value:
CASE WHEN ISNULL("EKPO"."LOEKZ") = 1 THEN 'not deleted'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'S' THEN 'locked'
     WHEN "EKPO"."LOEKZ" = 'L' THEN 'deleted'
     ELSE "EKPO"."LOEKZ"
END

variables.name: filter6
variables.value:
CASE
    WHEN ISNULL("LFA1"."VBUND") = 1 THEN 'External'
    ELSE 'Internal'
END

variables.name: rework_activities

variables.name: change_activities
variables.value: 'Change Currency','Change Delivery Indicator','Change Final Invoice Indicator','Change Price','Change Quantity','Change Storage Location','Change Vendor'

variables.name: B_KPI
variables.value: AVG( CASE          WHEN ISNULL(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) = 1 THEN NULL         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 AND DAYS_BETWEEN(TODAY(),<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>) >= 0 THEN 1.0         WHEN ISNULL(<%= GR_VARIABLE %>) = 1 THEN 0.0         WHEN DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) <= 0         AND  DAYS_BETWEEN(<%= ANALYSIS_KPI %>, <%= GR_VARIABLE %>) >= -3     THEN 1.0      ELSE 0.0      END )

sheetFilter.text:
FILTER PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Goods Receipt') > 0; 
FILTER PU_COUNT("EKPO", "_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN","_CEL_P2P_ACTIVITIES"."ACTIVITY_EN" = 'Record Invoice Receipt') > 0;
